  "title": "🦅 Sales & Talent Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br />Step into a role that combines energy, strategy, and people! ⚡ Join Euphoria Organization as a Sales & Talent Coordinator and play a key role in driving sales while recruiting top talent. It’s a fast-paced, rewarding environment perfect for fresh graduates looking to grow.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Meet sales targets and develop client relationships 💼</p></li><li><p>Source, interview, and onboard talented candidates</p></li><li><p>Assist in planning recruitment campaigns and initiatives 💡</p></li><li><p>Support the team with creative ideas and solutions</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Fresh graduates or early career professionals</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Energetic, motivated, and team-player mindset</p></li></ul><p><strong>Perks:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Mentorship and professional development</p></li><li><p>Team events and bonding activities 🎉</p></li><li><p>Career growth opportunities in a dynamic environment</p></li></ul>",
